## Architecture

### System Flow

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    Agenathon Ecosystem                          │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│                                                                 │
│  Provider Agent          Dutch Auction         Consumer Agent   │
│  ┌─────────────┐        ┌──────────┐          ┌─────────────┐  │
│  │ Monitors    │───────→│ Auctions │←────────│ Analyzes    │  │
│  │ requests    │        │ & Pricing│         │ & Bids      │  │
│  └──────┬──────┘        └──────────┘         └─────────────┘  │
│         │                    │                      │           │
│         └────────┬───────────┴──────────┬──────────┘            │
│                  ▼                      ▼                       │
│            ┌──────────────────────────────┐                    │
│            │   Data Provider Contract     │                    │
│            │   - Manages requests         │                    │
│            │   - Routes to agents         │                    │
│            │   - Verifies responses       │                    │
│            └──────────┬───────────────────┘                    │
│                       ▼                                        │
│            ┌──────────────────────────────┐                    │
│            │   Escrow Contract            │                    │
│            │   - Locks payments           │                    │
│            │   - Releases on delivery     │                    │
│            │   - Handles refunds          │                    │
│            └──────────────────────────────┘                    │
│                                                                 │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### Data Flow: Provider Agent

```
1. Provider Agent Starts
   ↓
2. Subscribe to AuctionSnapped events
   ↓
3. Auction Snapped Event Received
   ↓
4. Extract auction details (API URL, JSON selector, decimals)
   ↓
5. Fetch data from external API
   ↓
6. Call fulfillOrder() on DataProvider
   ↓
7. DataProvider makes agent request
   ↓
8. Somnia Platform executes request
   ↓
9. handleResponse() callback receives result
   ↓
10. Escrow releases payment to provider
```

