## Troubleshooting

### Common Issues

#### 1. Agent Not Receiving Events

Problem: Provider agent doesn't see AuctionSnapped events

Solutions:
```typescript
// Check RPC connection
const balance = await provider.getBalance(wallet.address);
console.log("Balance:", ethers.formatEther(balance));

// Verify contract address
const code = await provider.getCode(dutchAuctionAddress);
if (code === "0x") {
  console.error("Contract not found at address!");
}

// Check network
const network = await provider.getNetwork();
console.log("Connected to:", network.name, network.chainId);
```

#### 2. Transaction Fails with "Insufficient Deposit"

Problem: fulfillOrder reverts with insufficient deposit

Solution: Increase the deposit calculation
```typescript
const SUBCOMMITTEE_SIZE = 3n;
const PER_AGENT_EXECUTION_COST = ethers.parseEther("0.03");
const requestDeposit = await dataProviderContract.getRequestDeposit();

// Add buffer for price fluctuations
const buffer = ethers.parseEther("0.1");
const totalDeposit = requestDeposit + 
  (PER_AGENT_EXECUTION_COST * SUBCOMMITTEE_SIZE) + 
  buffer;
```

#### 3. Consumer Agent Never Bids

Problem: Consumer agent sees auctions but doesn't execute snaps

Solutions:
```typescript
// Check budget
console.log("Budget:", ethers.formatEther(config.consumerBudgetWei));
console.log("Current price:", ethers.formatEther(auction.currentPrice));

// Verify gas estimation
const gasEstimate = await dutchAuctionContract.snap.estimateGas(auctionId, {
  value: auction.currentPrice,
});
console.log("Estimated gas:", gasEstimate.toString());

// Check AI decision-making
const shouldBid = await agent.shouldBidOnAuction(auction);
console.log("AI Decision:", shouldBid);
```

#### 4. HuggingFace API Rate Limiting

Problem: "429 Too Many Requests" from HuggingFace

Solution: Implement backoff and caching
```typescript
const axiosRetry = require("axios-retry");

axiosRetry(this.huggingFaceClient, {
  retries: 3,
  retryDelay: axiosRetry.exponentialDelay,
  retryCondition: (error) => {
    return axiosRetry.isNetworkOrIdempotentReuqestError(error) ||
           error.response?.status === 429;
  },
});
```

#### 5. Out of Gas Errors

Problem: Transactions fail with "out of gas"

Solutions:
```typescript
// Increase gas limits
const tx = await contract.someFunction({
  gasLimit: 5000000,  // Increase from default
});

// Use eth_estimateGas
const gasEstimate = await provider.estimateGas({
  to: contractAddress,
  data: encodedData,
});

// Add safety margin
const finalGas = (gasEstimate * 120n) / 100n;  // 20% buffer
```

